Now what is left to be determined is the function . In fact it 
is the goal of the Dijkgraaf-Vafa's proposal to identify  as the
free energy of an auxiliary nonsupersymmetric matrix model which has for
its ordinary potential  the same function  that is the superpotential
of the four dimensional supersymmetric gauge theory. The matrix model free 
energy is given by
